SuperTux 0.3.0, aka Milestone 1.9, was released on 2006-12-17. At the time of this writing, only a source package and an autopackage are available with a Windows version shortly to follow. 

Download Milestone 1.9 from developer.berlios.de/project/showfiles.php?group_id=3467&release_id=11879.


